n%3D35769%26snA%3D1416%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a79d38e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=35769&amp;snA=1416&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=</a>"},{"pid":"70b5a620a63508bcc07b9d3ff802fa769805cb7e","tid":2057493,"uid":33938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"1001唔撚開post屌佢老母"},{"pid":"95005b82fd78fc649140df6cc047389786b4edf8","tid":2057493,"uid":84882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"戰鬥匹配規則<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定了匹到的公會以後選擇該公會的哪個玩家進行戰鬥<br />\n1.戰鬥規則:(1)無法選擇攻擊對象的自動匹配<br />\n                  (2)一天進行1次<br />\n                  (3)1次戰鬥總進行3回合<br />\n                  (4)各回合與敵公會的其他對手戰鬥<br />\n2.戰鬥規則(1)3回合中輸一次時戰鬥失敗<br />\n                 (2)過回合的時候英雄的HP回滿<br />\n                 (3)過回合的時候死亡的英雄不會覆活<br />\n                 (4)強制結束時消耗入場券,處理為失敗<br />\n                 (5)準備時間可編成隊伍(但不可以進行裝備更換,升級等)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隊伍編成禁止英雄<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公會戰可設定每周的禁止英雄</span></span></strong><br />\n下一個周次的禁止英雄不會告訴給玩家<br />\n上一周編成的英雄為這周的禁止英雄時無法準備<br />\n<br />\n計算分數<br />\n組合:為了周結算決定的公會組合<br />\n按照一周的勝利次數決定R,S,A,B,C,D,E組合<br />\n參與:最少得有25名參加<br />\n        25名以後每1名獲得額外分數<br />\n成績:公會員個人的戰鬥勝利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579115c429197afcd3eb07d62c91521a51fa7259","tid":2057493,"uid":164464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59eee76440cdd2249bc9859683e515a2008cc507","tid":2057493,"uid":123869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知咩事爆左機<br />\n慢慢升戰力返9章拎星星"},"citedBy":0,"repl